    <header>About Thread&Co.</header>

    <div class="container">
      <div class="section">
        <h2>Who We Are</h2>
        <p>
          Thread&Co. is a modern men’s fashion eCommerce platform founded with
          one goal: to make stylish, versatile, and quality clothing easily
          accessible. We bring together casual, semi-formal, streetwear,
          traditional, and athleisure under one digital roof — offering a
          seamless shopping experience for today’s man.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="section">
        <h2>Our Vision</h2>
        <p>
          To be the go-to fashion platform for men seeking quality, style, and
          simplicity — blending modern design with comfort and cultural
          relevance.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="section">
        <h2>Our Mission</h2>
        <p>
          <span class="highlight">•</span> Deliver high-quality men’s clothing
          for every lifestyle and occasion. <br />
          <span class="highlight">•</span> Support local craftsmanship and
          empower communities in Nepal. <br />
          <span class="highlight">•</span> Design fashion that makes men feel
          confident, comfortable, and authentic. <br />
          <span class="highlight">•</span> Provide a smooth and enjoyable online
          shopping experience.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="section">
        <h2>Our Journey</h2>
        <p>
          Thread&Co. began as a college passion project, combining a love for
          tech with fashion. Since then, it has grown into a full-fledged
          platform, proudly built and operated from Nepal — connecting culture,
          comfort, and style.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="section">
        <h2>Why Choose Us?</h2>
        <p>
          From bold streetwear to subtle classics, every Thread&Co. collection
          is created with purpose. We focus on quality fabrics, smart design,
          and ethical practices — so you can shop confidently knowing your
          outfit stands for something bigger.
        </p>
      </div>
